I was distracted

317
00:28:56,130 --> 00:28:57,793
Distracted?

318
00:28:58,808 --> 00:29:02,400
Yes, I was thinking about things

319
00:29:05,615 --> 00:29:06,616
And?

320
00:29:26,598 --> 00:29:28,789
Ok. Leave it alone. It doesn't matter

321
00:29:29,684 --> 00:29:31,621
I can see you don't want to
talk about it either

322
00:29:32,060 --> 00:29:33,612
No. I'm just remembering

323
00:29:54,255 --> 00:29:59,202
When I realized I was in the air,
jumping on an almost empty pool

324
00:30:08,369 --> 00:30:13,434
- Were you left unconscious?
- No. I was just there...face down

325
00:30:14,153 --> 00:30:15,345
Floating

326
00:30:19,456 --> 00:30:21,968
You know is true what they say about those
that are about to die

327
00:30:22,176 --> 00:30:26,088
that all of a sudden you get to see the
most important moments of your life

328
00:30:26,848 --> 00:30:27,951
That happened to me

329
00:30:30,815 --> 00:30:32,111
