I'm talking about me, Ramon Sampedro

350
00:33:52,445 --> 00:33:54,317
There are other ways of making love

351
00:33:54,540 --> 00:33:55,764
Yes of course

352
00:34:02,115 --> 00:34:04,788
Has any girl kissed you in the past 27 years?

353
